Rump, fillet and T-Bone are the most popular cuts of beef when eating out . 
  55 per cent of us cook beef at home and rely on burgers or mince . 
  Sirloin, topside and fillet are best saved for the roasting pan . 
  When stewing go for brisket, shoulder and ribs . 
